FBIS4-68121 "jptot020__l94043" JPRS-TOT-94-020-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 9 May 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA INDIA Two Bombs Explode at Officials' Homes in Sikkim Two Bombs Explode at Officials' Homes in Sikkim BK0905102094 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0830 GMT 9 May 94 BK0905102094 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] In Sikkim, two bombs exploded at the residence of the state power minister and the former chief secretary. The director general of police, Mr. P.S. Bawa, told PTI today that the power minister, Mr. B.B. Subba, was not at his residence when the explosion took place last night. Another bomb was hurled at the residence of the former chief secretary, Mr. P.K. Pradhan, in the early hours yesterday. The explosions, however, did not cause much damage.
